{"tid":505620,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【禽獸校園】男學生遭強吻舔胸 中學阿sir被舉報","createTime":"2017-12-21T10:10:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-21T10:41:19.000Z","uid":48093,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8b9776e253d896139daf22224fa71f1309a73fb7","tid":505620,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T10:10:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171221/large/1513847642_34bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171221%2Flarge%2F1513847642_34bd.jpg&h=521c22d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地再爆教師涉嫌猥褻學生事件。四川成都市蜀興職業中學（四川省成都市第三十中學）官方微博今日通報，有網友爆料，指成都蜀興職業中學一男教師涉嫌猥褻男生。校方回應，接到舉報後，已將該男教師停職進行調查。<br />\n<br />\n據《法制晚報》報道，網友「澤軒君」爆料，指四川省成都市蜀興職業中學德育處主任男性教師朱成軍，對該校多名男學生進行猥褻、性騷擾。其中一名同學甚至遭受朱成軍自2016年夏始至今，長達一年半時期間，朱成軍車內或家中該名學生強行接吻、脫衣、摟抱、撫摸敏感隱私部位、舔胸等不正當接觸。該學生站出來揭露朱成軍的惡行，希望其他受害的同學也能夠積極站出來揭露。<br />\n<br />\n校方今日於官方微博發帖，已將該朱姓教師停職停課，配合組織調查。"},{"pid":"0a9d516d9501edddff2172e52723e9d970fdf1aa","tid":505620,"uid":35129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T10:13:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">THIS</span></span>"},{"pid":"3e2d373c689370be57ab5a7547cc71d2103fd554","tid":505620,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T10:15:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f9c5775f5adbdb32488f0feb93eba26514f36eb","tid":505620,"uid":43770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T10:19:10.000Z","msg":"硬左"},{"pid":"4c13fb495cfefd36beee15d7ab9815e19210da10","tid":505620,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T10:20:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>硬左</blockquote><br />\nFBI is watching u<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb2b5992d491a3b2374dc3439f5400993705c008","tid":505620,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T10:21:07.000Z","msg":"強吻影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca69b04d54c5eb306689b3b36ae94f2390b2a85a","tid":505620,"uid":48093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T10:41:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>強吻影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}